<div class="com-share" data-id="20288" data-title="《这个超市视频广告有毒，慎入》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20288/medium/20288.gif?1451996689" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20288.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
